      `Account Security: You are strictly responsible for safeguarding your password and any other credentials used to access your account.`,
    ],
  },
  {
    navLabel: 'Ecosystem Affiliates',
    title: 'Ecosystem Affiliates and Strategic Partners',
    updated: 'Updated April 17, 2026',
    heading: 'Ecosystem Affiliates and Strategic Partners',
    content: [
