    ],
  },
  {
    navLabel: 'User Conduct',
    title: 'User Conduct and Acceptable Use',
    updated: 'Updated April 17, 2026',
    heading: 'User Conduct and Acceptable Use',
    content: [
      `Workglobal maintains a professional, equitable, and highly efficient ecosystem. You agree NOT to engage in any of the following prohibited activities:`,
      `The Anti-Ghosting Protocol: Workglobal is built on rapid communication. If an Employer or Jobseeker repeatedly matches and initiates chats but fails to respond for extended periods ("ghosting"), Workglobal reserves the right to algorithmically penalize the user’s profile visibility or suspend the account.`,
      `Fraud and Misrepresentation: Creating fake profiles, posting fraudulent job listings, misrepresenting your qualifications, or impersonating another person or business entity is strictly prohibited and will result in immediate account termination.`,
      `Data Scraping: You may not use automated scripts, bots, spiders, or scrapers to extract data, candidate profiles, or job listings from the Platform.`,
      `Discrimination and Harassment: You may not use the Platform's messaging system to harass, abuse, or discriminate against any user based on race, gender, religion, national origin, disability, or sexual orientation.`,
    ],
  },
  {
    navLabel: 'Subscriptions & Payments',
    title: 'Subscriptions, Fees, and Payments',
    updated: 'Updated April 17, 2026',
    heading: 'Subscriptions, Fees, and Payments',
    content: [
      `Workglobal offers both free and premium subscription tiers for users.`,
      `Billing and Renewal: Premium subscriptions are billed on a recurring basis depending on your selected plan. By providing payment information, you authorize Workglobal (via our third-party payment processors) to charge the applicable fees automatically.`,
      `No Refunds: All subscription fees, job posting credits, and in-app purchases are non-refundable. If you cancel your subscription, you will retain access to the premium features until the end of your current billing cycle.`,
    ],
  },
  {
    navLabel: 'Intellectual Property',
    title: 'Intellectual Property Rights',
    updated: 'Updated April 17, 2026',
    heading: 'Intellectual Property Rights',
    content: [
      `Workglobal's IP: All content, design, graphics, algorithms, underlying code, and trademarks (including "Workglobal", "Swipe. Match. Work.", and the Workglobal logos) are the exclusive property of Resource Pool Group Ltd. You are granted a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use the Platform for its intended purpose.`,
