      `Any dispute arising out of or in connection with these Terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of London, United Kingdom. Due to our global operations, we reserve the right to seek injunctive relief in any jurisdiction where we deem it necessary to protect our intellectual property or operational security.`,
